      "comment": "TARYN'S BLUE (7) flew the lids from out wide with a slick early split but ran over at the finish when a narrow fourth (17.07) over 300m at this track. Better than last start and worth following up. ASTON ROCHELLE (1) has been mixing form lately, hitting the frame two back before finishing sixth (19.67) at this track in a R/A FIN. Rates a winning chance on best. SAILAWAY GIN (3) turned in a fair 5th placed finish last time at this track over 300m (17.10). Form here at the trip sound including nine wins. The form out of her last race has been franked. Has ability and is one of the better chances. PAW HARKONNEN (2) drops in distance and is not to be underestimated.",
